Summary: Orange and Rockland Utility Smart Energy Meter
Home-page: http://github.com/bvlaicu/oru/
Author: Bogdan Vlaicu
Author-email: bogdanvlaicu@yahoo.com
License: Apache Software License
Description: Oru calls the API of the Orange and Rockland Utility smart energy meter to return the current energy usage.
        
        It requires the meter id.
        
        Example usage:
            oru.get_last_meter_read_wh("701139904")
        
        
